<title>ạlnhạrdẗ ywm mylạd ʿylẗ jdydẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạlnhạrdẗ ywm mylạd ʿylẗ jdydẗ

[V2]
 ạ̹nt ạlly btbạrkhhạ bʿṭạyạ wmḥbẗ ạ̉kydẗ

[V3]
 1- ḥbk dạymaⁿạ yjmʿhm bslạm tkwn wsṭyhm

[V4]
 ạ̹nt tḍmn ḥyạthm wrwḥk yskn fyhm

[V5]
 2- ʿrwstnạ wʿrysnạ bnsybhm byn ạ̹ydyk

[V6]
 wḥyạthm kl ywm tsẖhd ʿnk yạ mlyk

[V7]
 3- ʿạyzyn nsẖwf frḥhm ḥy dạymaⁿạ kl ywm

[V8]
 msẖ bs ykwn lynạ dẖkry̱ ạ̉w ṣwrẗ fy ạ̉lbwm</lyrics>
</song>